Package: gbifexplorer
Type: Package
Title: Explore DarwinCore Archives and generates friendly coverage summaries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  c(
    person("Antonio Jesús", "Pérez-Luque", , "ajpelu@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1747-0469"))
           )
Description: The package use DarwinCore Archives and computes summaries for the 
    spatial, temporal and taxonomical coverages. It also generates friendly reports 
    for taxonomic coverage to be used as part of Data Papers.
